589
00:28:51,050 --> 00:28:52,530
I have an empty house.

590
00:28:52,530 --> 00:28:53,300
I can…

591
00:28:54,090 --> 00:28:55,010
What can you do?

592
00:28:55,090 --> 00:28:56,060
I can live there.

593
00:28:56,130 --> 00:28:57,300
