606
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:24,330
You as a Disney princess?

607
00:29:25,490 --> 00:29:26,500
What a pity.

608
00:29:26,530 --> 00:29:27,590
In someone's eyes,

609
00:29:28,090 --> 00:29:30,610
I'm just an annoying supporting actor.

610
00:29:33,250 --> 00:29:34,130
How come?

611
00:29:34,570 --> 00:29:35,170
Mr. Ji,

612
00:29:35,330 --> 00:29:36,290
from now on,

613
00:29:36,340 --> 00:29:37,470
you're my male lead.

614
00:30:05,340 --> 00:30:06,870
