615
00:30:07,090 --> 00:30:09,340
are the same as my novel.

616
00:30:11,290 --> 00:30:12,570
This house has been vacant.

617
00:30:12,570 --> 00:30:14,900
It has all the necessary home appliances.

618
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:16,610
Mr. Ji,

619
00:30:16,900 --> 00:30:18,410
you aren't going to say

620
00:30:18,650 --> 00:30:20,570
that you live next door,

621
00:30:20,810 --> 00:30:21,270
are you?

622
00:30:21,650 --> 00:30:23,130
I live next door.

623
00:30:24,130 --> 00:30:25,650
You own both the units on the same floor?

624
00:30:25,650 --> 00:30:26,890
Are you rich people

625
00:30:27,090 --> 00:30:28,420
