626
00:30:28,420 --> 00:30:29,810
You don't even live here.

627
00:30:29,810 --> 00:30:32,050
You'll only come when you're in a good mood.

628
00:30:32,050 --> 00:30:33,660
Are you complimenting me or scolding me?

629
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:34,720
It's a compliment.

630
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:36,330
Of course.

631
00:30:37,710 --> 00:30:39,140
Compared to you,

632
00:30:39,150 --> 00:30:40,450
