633
00:30:40,490 --> 00:30:41,660
Since it's stamp collecting,

634
00:30:41,660 --> 00:30:42,900
I have to keep it well.

635
00:30:43,050 --> 00:30:43,910
I won't rent it.

636
00:30:44,330 --> 00:30:46,260
Mr. Ji, I'm sorry.

637
00:30:49,770 --> 00:30:50,860
You are silent.

638
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:53,000
I'll take it as your forgiveness.

639
00:30:53,620 --> 00:30:55,060
I annoyed him so much,

640
00:30:55,300 --> 00:30:57,560
