641
00:30:57,730 --> 00:30:59,610
Does he really like me?

642
00:30:59,850 --> 00:31:00,890
No way.

643
00:31:03,730 --> 00:31:04,410
Mr. Ji,

644
00:31:04,850 --> 00:31:07,090
