645
00:31:07,330 --> 00:31:08,790
You don't have to respond.

646
00:31:09,050 --> 00:31:11,050
I know there's a huge gap between us.

647
00:31:11,060 --> 00:31:12,810
I expect nothing from this crush.

648
00:31:12,810 --> 00:31:13,810
It just occurred to me that

649
00:31:13,810 --> 00:31:15,530
I have other uses for this apartment.

650
00:31:15,530 --> 00:31:16,650
