If we become neighbors,

656
00:31:24,170 --> 00:31:26,250
we will always meet each other.

657
00:31:26,450 --> 00:31:27,460
Then we can't forget each other.

658
00:31:27,460 --> 00:31:28,930
So, let's keep a distance.

659
00:31:29,050 --> 00:31:29,850
Mr. Ji,

660
00:31:29,850 --> 00:31:30,850
I know I was wrong.

661
00:31:31,130 --> 00:31:32,410
I shouldn't give up my love for you

662
00:31:32,410 --> 00:31:34,070
