666
00:31:38,650 --> 00:31:40,050
I'll never part from you.

667
00:31:44,020 --> 00:31:44,530
But I...

668
00:31:44,530 --> 00:31:45,290
No buts.

669
00:31:45,530 --> 00:31:47,250
I like you.

670
00:31:50,980 --> 00:31:51,810
Well,

671
00:31:53,020 --> 00:31:54,500
if you're not busy,

672
00:31:54,530 --> 00:31:56,730
