691
00:32:45,810 --> 00:32:46,650
Sister.

692
00:32:46,650 --> 00:32:47,690
Okay, sister.

693
00:32:48,060 --> 00:32:49,850
Then give her a name.

694
00:32:52,700 --> 00:32:53,210
Fei.

695
00:32:53,530 --> 00:32:56,170
