696
00:32:56,770 --> 00:32:58,290
I'm asking you, Ji Shu.

697
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:00,460
Ji Fei.

698
00:33:02,010 --> 00:33:04,970
I'm asking you why your artist Ye Xining

699
00:33:05,090 --> 00:33:06,850
