700
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:09,260
I'm not with Ye Xining.

701
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:11,010
I mean Yu Le.

702
00:33:11,340 --> 00:33:11,850
Yu Le?

703
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:12,970
Brother.

704
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:14,570
You're my brother.

705
00:33:14,610 --> 00:33:16,490
Can you make your artist Ye Xining

706
00:33:16,530 --> 00:33:17,250
