709
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:25,370
Do you think I'm an emperor who can dictate others' relationships?

710
00:33:25,370 --> 00:33:26,290
Who are you?

711
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:27,720
None of your business.

712
00:33:28,250 --> 00:33:28,830
I...

713
00:33:29,130 --> 00:33:30,530
