714
00:33:30,530 --> 00:33:31,970
She's my employee.

715
00:33:32,780 --> 00:33:35,300
I'll let her stay in the other apartment temporarily.

716
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:35,970
It's legal.

717
00:33:37,580 --> 00:33:38,530
But you're not

718
00:33:38,530 --> 00:33:40,100
