727
00:33:55,290 --> 00:33:56,940
She's an artist of the company.

728
00:33:56,940 --> 00:33:58,580
She didn't sell herself to the company.

729
00:33:58,580 --> 00:33:59,660
Whatever.

730
00:33:59,660 --> 00:34:01,250
Just make them break up.

731
00:34:01,540 --> 00:34:03,620
How can she be with my idol?

732
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:05,330
Because it's true love.

733
00:34:06,090 --> 00:34:06,690
True love?

734
00:34:06,980 --> 00:34:08,530
Do you know what true love is?

735
00:34:08,530 --> 00:34:09,370
You know?

736
00:34:09,570 --> 00:34:11,100
Ji Fei, you should be tired.

737
00:34:11,530 --> 00:34:12,530
Go to bed early.

738
00:34:12,530 --> 00:34:14,190
What kind of employee are you?

739
00:34:14,570 --> 00:34:15,730
It's no use arguing with your brother.

740
00:34:15,730 --> 00:34:17,330
It's true love between them.

741
00:34:19,969 --> 00:34:20,830
He has a sister,

742
00:34:21,170 --> 00:34:22,010
Ji Fei?

743
00:34:27,889 --> 00:34:29,690
Hello, everyone. I'm back.

744
00:34:29,900 --> 00:34:31,290
Stop your work.

745
00:34:31,290 --> 00:34:33,530
Look. I've brought you gifts.

746
00:34:33,610 --> 00:34:35,010
Fei, great!

747
00:34:35,050 --> 00:34:35,980
You're finally back.

748
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:37,969
Finally, someone can gossip with me.

749
00:34:37,969 --> 00:34:38,900
I want to ask you.

750
00:34:39,170 --> 00:34:42,090
Someone in the company has had a crush on my brother for ten years.

751
00:34:42,090 --> 00:34:43,010
Really?

752
00:34:43,130 --> 00:34:43,940
Who is it?

753
00:34:44,449 --> 00:34:45,449
It's been ten years.

754
00:34:45,449 --> 00:34:46,530
Well…

755
00:34:48,610 --> 00:34:49,250
You?

756
00:34:51,100 --> 00:34:54,429
