760
00:35:02,690 --> 00:35:03,550
How old are you?

761
00:35:03,850 --> 00:35:05,210
We should be about the same age.

762
00:35:05,210 --> 00:35:07,470
Maybe we were in the same grade at school.

763
00:35:08,170 --> 00:35:09,140
But how come I don't remember you

764
00:35:09,140 --> 00:35:11,020
