768
00:35:18,610 --> 00:35:19,470
One-sided love

769
00:35:19,890 --> 00:35:21,250
is always silent.

770
00:35:22,090 --> 00:35:22,930
At that time,

771
00:35:23,130 --> 00:35:24,290
I was inferior.

772
00:35:24,530 --> 00:35:25,650
I was embarrassed to see him.

773
00:35:25,650 --> 00:35:26,530
Inferior…

774
00:35:27,290 --> 00:35:30,570
Compared to those girls who had a crush on my brother,

775
00:35:30,690 --> 00:35:32,290
