782
00:35:47,690 --> 00:35:49,170
Then he and Xining...

783
00:35:49,290 --> 00:35:50,010
Xining?

784
00:35:51,090 --> 00:35:52,570
It's just a crush.

785
00:35:52,690 --> 00:35:53,770
Who can be sure

786
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:54,900
