787
00:35:55,410 --> 00:35:56,810
It's none of my business.

788
00:35:56,890 --> 00:35:58,950
How about I help you chase my brother?

789
00:36:01,570 --> 00:36:03,700
You betrayed your brother so quickly?

790
00:36:03,810 --> 00:36:05,140
