795
00:36:13,210 --> 00:36:13,930
Forget it.

796
00:36:14,420 --> 00:36:15,480
Do you need my help?

797
00:36:17,890 --> 00:36:18,690
Sure.

798
00:36:19,060 --> 00:36:20,010
Let me tell you

799
00:36:20,170 --> 00:36:22,030
what kind of person my brother is.

800
00:36:22,490 --> 00:36:24,740
Although he looks serious

801
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:26,180
and he's a fashionable president,

802
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:27,050
in fact,

803
00:36:27,370 --> 00:36:28,500
he's just old-school.

804
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,230
Old-school?

805
00:36:30,290 --> 00:36:35,420
All he does every day is playing mahjong.

806
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:35,890
I won.

807
00:36:36,130 --> 00:36:36,700
Mahjong.

808
00:36:37,050 --> 00:36:37,940
Tai Chi.

809
00:36:38,050 --> 00:36:38,780
Surprised?

810
00:36:39,250 --> 00:36:40,450
I didn't expect that.

811
00:36:40,530 --> 00:36:42,380
He's so similar to the writer.

812
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:45,740
Don't feel inferior.

813
00:36:46,340 --> 00:36:47,000
From now on,

814
00:36:47,250 --> 00:36:48,250
feel free to ask me

815
00:36:48,330 --> 00:36:49,860
anything about my brother.

816
00:36:50,780 --> 00:36:51,510
