822
00:37:09,570 --> 00:37:11,170
We can't co-exist under the same roof.

823
00:37:11,170 --> 00:37:11,570
I...

824
00:37:11,890 --> 00:37:13,620
I'll ask my brother to fire you.

825
00:37:15,980 --> 00:37:16,610
Brother.

826
00:37:18,650 --> 00:37:19,740
Fire her.

827
00:37:24,530 --> 00:37:25,620
Mr. Ji,

828
00:37:26,610 --> 00:37:29,970
I believe you can distinguish personal stuff from business.

829
00:37:29,970 --> 00:37:30,660
Don't worry.

830
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:31,990
They won't be together.

831
00:37:32,930 --> 00:37:33,580
Really?

832
00:37:34,610 --> 00:37:35,170
