834
00:37:37,820 --> 00:37:38,350
Fire her.

835
00:37:38,420 --> 00:37:39,260
I can't fire her.

836
00:37:39,260 --> 00:37:40,210
From now on,

837
00:37:40,300 --> 00:37:41,250
