841
00:37:48,210 --> 00:37:48,700
Right.

842
00:37:48,810 --> 00:37:50,180
Why should I be your assistant?

843
00:37:50,180 --> 00:37:51,660
I don't think I can do this job.

844
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:52,010
I…

845
00:37:52,090 --> 00:37:54,180
Mr. Ji, what makes you think I'm capable? I'll change.

846
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:54,770
I'm with her.

847
00:37:54,770 --> 00:37:56,570
She's incapable from top to bottom, from left to right.

848
00:37:56,570 --> 00:37:57,170
That's right.

849
00:37:57,170 --> 00:37:57,770
Fei.

850
00:37:57,890 --> 00:38:00,820
If you don't have anything to do, go play by yourself.

851
00:38:00,850 --> 00:38:01,410
Mr. Ji,

852
00:38:01,570 --> 00:38:02,330
