853
00:38:02,330 --> 00:38:03,210
I don't agree.

854
00:38:03,250 --> 00:38:03,980
I'm the boss.

855
00:38:04,090 --> 00:38:04,930
You're an employee.

856
00:38:04,930 --> 00:38:06,060
