857
00:38:14,250 --> 00:38:14,850
Mr. Ji,

858
00:38:15,850 --> 00:38:17,690
I can't do this job.

859
00:38:17,930 --> 00:38:19,450
You know,

860
00:38:19,450 --> 00:38:20,730
